metadata.name: Efflorescence #77
metadata.description:
Efflorescence is a piece that bridges between Pouya and Fatima's hand crafted tiles and Gorilla Sun's generative work, and reflects their collective love for patterns and colour. Efflorescence is a generative token that creates unique compositions by random arrangement of different tiles and the colorisation thereof.

This generative token would not have been possible without Zeno Zeng's SVG runtime for P5JS!

Press the down arrow button to export an SVG of the artwork. In live view stroke width can be adjusted by zooming in and out.

metadata.name: We Are Alone Together #187
metadata.description:
We meander through the flows of life, alone but together. This experience — an ultimately solitary one — is communicated but never truly shared. Our consciousnesses live in a perpetual separated state, alone but together.

############

Display resolution scales with window size. Press ’h’ (in live mode) to generate a 6000x7500 hi-res image. This may take a few seconds to generate depending on your hardware. Press ‘d’ to redraw the artwork.

Original artwork by perkwerk * made with p5.js * 2022

metadata.name: Mandaloids #22
metadata.description:
Note that these pieces render progressively via pathtracing in WebGL, so will take some time to converge to the final image.

Pan and zoom interactively to exlore detail. The camera focus adjusts automatically. Zoom the browser window (Ctrl key + "-") to render at higher resolution (and "P" to save the image).

metadata.name: 13 ukrainians #6
metadata.description:
Dedicated to 13 border guards on the Snake Island, Ukraine.
Each token has 13 petals, they represent guards, warships are scattered in random "fuck off" directions.
Wiki article about this event: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian_warship,_go_fuck_yourself

100% of sales will go to the frontline squad, to the guys who defend Kyiv right now.
N - to remove warships.
O - to be able to change perspective.
